headline: 1 Internet Stock on Our Buy List and 2 We Avoid
summary: Consumer internet businesses are redefining how people engage with the world by giving them instant connectivity and convenience. This influence cuts both ways though because they have high exposure to the ups and downs of consumer spending, and uncertainty surrounding this factor has capped the industry’s returns - over the past six months, its 9.4% gain has lagged the S&P 500 by 7 percentage points.
